How to pass JVM parameters to the roboRIO? Java
I am trying to attach a VisualVM profiler to the roboRIO with some success. I want to be able to modify the gradle.build file to pass the JVM parameters down to the roboRIO so I can attach it via JMX. I haven’t been able to find any such documentation. Can anyone help with this?
